@startuml
' @id(SEQ-RUN-CYCLE)
' @ref(USE-RUN-CYCLE)
'
' Current-side flow as implemented by the /mdd-cycle skill
' (templates::MDD_CYCLE_SKILL). The skill is agent-driven; mdd-core
' supplies the read-side (CycleRegistry) and the manifest schema.
'
' @desc(SEQ-RUN-CYCLE, "As-built /mdd-cycle orchestration: pick entry, open cycle + snapshot before/, loop validate->implement->map->validate->review, then close + snapshot after/ + write diff.")
title Run a full MDD cycle from one description (current)

actor "Developer" as Dev
participant "/mdd-cycle\n(SKILL.md)" as Orch
database ".mdd/cycles/<N>/\nmanifest.yml, before/, after/" as Store
participant "/mdd-generate\nor /mdd-map" as Entry
participant "/mdd-validate" as Val
participant "/mdd-implement" as Impl
participant "/mdd-map" as Map
participant "/mdd-review" as Rev

Dev -> Orch : /mdd-cycle [description?]

alt description provided
  Orch -> Orch : entry = generate
else no description
  Orch -> Orch : entry = map (no comments)\nrefresh use-case view, then STOP
end

Orch -> Store : mkdir .mdd/cycles/<N>/\ncopy current/ -> before/\nwrite manifest.yml (status: open)
Store --> Orch : cycle N opened

Orch -> Entry : run entry skill (scoped)
Entry --> Orch : models written (+ @desc per @id)

loop until /mdd-review parity matches
  Orch -> Val : /mdd-validate
  Val --> Orch : clean / errors

  opt decision genuinely ambiguous
    Orch -> Dev : ask clarifying question
    Dev --> Orch : answer
    note right of Orch
      Mandatory pause documented in SKILL.md:
      never guess; block on the user.
    end note
  end

  Orch -> Impl : /mdd-implement
  Impl --> Orch : code changed
  Orch -> Map : /mdd-map (refresh current + @desc)
  Map --> Orch : current refreshed
  Orch -> Val : /mdd-validate
  Val --> Orch : clean
  Orch -> Rev : /mdd-review (ID + security parity)
  alt mismatch
    Rev --> Orch : .diff.puml
  else match
    Rev --> Orch : parity closed
  end
end

Orch -> Store : copy current/ -> after/\nwrite <diagram>.diff.puml\nmanifest status: closed + closed_at + touched_files
Store --> Orch : cycle N closed
Orch --> Dev : cycle N complete
@enduml
